OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny residual
OL,6,Fshowers quickly fading to leave a dry
OL,7,Fnight with long clear spells, and
OL,8,Fwinds becoming generally light.
OL,9,FTurning cold with a slight frost
OL,10,Fdeveloping in many places.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FStarting chilly with an early
OL,13,Fslight frost. A dry day to follow with
OL,14,Fvariable cloud but also bright spells
OL,15,Fat times. Generally light winds, with
OL,16,Ftemperatures rising just above average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
