OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FChilly
OL,6,Fstart Tuesday, then fine with warm
OL,7,Fsunshine and breezier, but cooler
OL,8,Fwhere any onshore winds. Warm and
OL,9,Fbright Wednesday, cloudier later.
OL,10,FThursday, cooler and breezy with
OL,11,Fsunshine and showers.
